signUp - Create new user account with email verification

signIn - Authenticate user with credentials (JWT generation)

signOut - Invalidate user session

resetPassword - Initiate password reset flow

updatePassword - Change authenticated user's password

verifyEmail - Confirm user's email address

refreshSession - Renew expired access token

updateUserRole - (Admin) Change user permissions

createDevice - Add new network device to monitoring

updateDevice - Modify device properties

deleteDevice - Remove device from monitoring

getDeviceStatus - Fetch current status of a device

bulkUpdateDevices - Update multiple devices at once

registerSwitch - Add new managed switch

updateSwitchConfig - Modify switch configuration

getSwitchPorts - Retrieve all ports for a switch

updatePortStatus - Update port status/configuration

fetchSwitchTopology - Get switch hierarchy/connections

logMonitoringData - Store device metrics (CPU, memory, bandwidth)

triggerDeviceScan - Initiate network discovery scan

forceStatusCheck - Manually ping specific device

getHistoricalMetrics - Fetch device performance history

updateDeviceStatus - (Python integration) Update status from monitoring scripts

createAlert - Generate new alert

resolveAlert - Mark alert as resolved

acknowledgeAlert - Confirm alert receipt

getActiveAlerts - Fetch unresolved alerts

configureAlertThresholds - Set alert trigger conditions

discoverNetwork - Auto-detect devices on network

mapNetworkTopology - Generate network connection diagram

backupSwitchConfig - Store switch configuration

restoreSwitchConfig - Apply saved configuration

fetchArpTable - Retrieve ARP data from switches

generateAvailabilityReport - Calculate uptime statistics

exportNetworkInventory - Export devices to CSV

getBandwidthUsage - Retrieve network utilization data

generateAuditLog - Create access history report

getAllUsers - (Admin) List all users

deactivateUser - (Admin) Disable user account

updateUserProfile - Modify user information